    • Method Detail

      • getGridDialect

        public GridDialect getGridDialect()
        Returns the current GridDialect.

        Intended for usage in code interacting with ORM SPIs which only provide access to the Dialect but not the service registry. Other code should obtain the grid dialect from the service registry.

        Returns:
        the current grid dialect.

      • getNativeIdentifierGeneratorClass

        public Class<? extends IdentifierGenerator> getNativeIdentifierGeneratorClass()

        Overridden in OGM in order to make things work when USE_NEW_ID_GENERATOR_MAPPINGS is set to false. If so, and if additionally the generation type is GenerationType.AUTO, the ORM engine will invoke this method to obtain the "native" identifier generator. Depending on the store's capabilities, OGM's identity, sequence or table generator will be returned.

        Overrides:
        getNativeIdentifierGeneratorClass in class Dialect
        See Also:
        AvailableSettings.USE_NEW_ID_GENERATOR_MAPPINGS
